data.description: Welcome to this charming end-unit townhome in the Ravenwood subdivision. This beautifully maintained home includes a primary bedroom conveniently located on the main level, complete with an ensuite bathroom for your comfort and privacy. A unique bonus to this property is the converted garage that provides extra space for your needs, whether it's a home office, gym, or additional storage. As you ascend to the second floor, you'll find a versatile loft area that can be adapted to your preferences, perfect for a study, play area, or cozy reading nook. The heart of this home is the stunning two-story living room, featuring an inviting fireplace that sets the perfect ambiance for those chilly evenings. Beyond the living room, you'll discover a delightful back deck area, ideal for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhome yours today!
